quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Maaku-aan nelaaɗo-eehey mon mon yedduɓe Alla."
  109,2,"Mi rewatah jooni wonah ko arata ko ndewaton ko e sanamuuji."
  109,3,"Onon ne on ndewatah Mbo ndewat Mi O, ko Oon woni Alla."
  109,4,"Mi wonah dewoowo ko ndewɗon e sanamuuji."
  109,5,"Onon ne on ndewatah Mbo ndewat Mi O ko Oon woni Alla."
  109,6,"Woodanii on diine mon mbo pepindaniɗon pittaali mon, woodanii kam diine mbo Alla tellini e Am."
  110,1,"Si ballal Alla diine ma arii-aan nelaaɗo- e semmbinde ma, uddital Makka laati."
  110,2,"Nji*a yimɓe na naata e diine Alla he pelle caggal pelle."
  110,3,"Anndu ɗum ko maande ɓadaade gasde ko takna Ma ko neleede, subhina e yettude joom Ma, yettude Mbo e neema e poolgu e uddital, yaafno Mbo, sabu ko keewɗo yaafaade jiyaaɓe Makko."
  111,1,"Halkiima juuɗe bappa nelaaɗo -yo o his- Abii laha biy Abdul Muttalibi e pertude golle makko, sabu ko loratno nelaaɗo, golle mum cooyi."
  111,2,"Hol ko jawdi mum nafi mbo? ndi ittanaani mbo lepte, ndi addanaani mbo yurmeende."
  111,3,"Ma o naat nyande darnga yiite nge lewlewndu, o tampa e nguleeki henge."
  111,4,"Ma debbo makko Ummu jamiil naat yiite sabu ko o loratno nelaaɗo-yo o his-weddaade gi*e e laawol makko."
  111,5,"Ina e daande makko ɓoggol moccangol haa tiiɗi o ɗowree ngol faade yiite."